references.paper_title: Autoforecast: Automatic time-series forecasting model selection

references.paper_title: Large language models are zero-shot reasoners
references.reason: This work introduced the "Let's think step by step" prompting technique that this paper is built upon.

references.paper_title: Gluonts: Probabilistic and neural time series modeling in python
references.reason: This work is a standard tool that provides various algorithms definitions and tools for time series forecasting.
This paper presents the popular Prophet forecasting model used as a baseline in the paper.

references.paper_title: Chain-of-thought prompting elicits reasoning in large language models
